subTitle: Himesh Reshammiya and Iulia Vantur are on the sets of The Kapil Sharma Show, to celebrate the success of their new album, Aap Se Mausiiquii. Himesh and Iulia had a fun time with Kapil and his crazy neighbours.

title: The Kapil Sharma Show
subTitle: Legendary musicians Kumar Sanu, Udit Narayan and Anuradha Paudwal are invited by Kapil Sharma for hilarious interactions and to discuss their renowned performances.

title: CID
subTitle: The CID team manage to identify the criminal mastermind who escapes to Paris. Soon, the team travels to France in order to continue their investigation and capture the mastermind.
